reviews.text:
Food quality is fair, service is not bad (on weekday), the tables arrangement could be better, suggest they can re-arrange it so that there can be more seats for customers. 

One more thing, there has smoking area outside, the door cannot resist smoke.

Went in on a busy Friday morning. As I'm a slow eater, I was constantly rushed by the lady boss because there are many more customers waiting for a seat outside. I understand her reason behind her actions, and I am trying my best to eat faster. Just made me not want to return anymore. The food isn't particularly good to justify being rushed out of the restaurant again.
Good
